/**
 * Transactional Email Templates
 *
 * Pre-built email templates for common SaaS scenarios.
 * Uses React Email for type-safe, component-based emails.
 *
 * Templates included:
 * - Welcome email (new user signup)
 * - Team invitation
 * - Password reset
 * - Payment failed
 * - Subscription updated
 * - Invoice/receipt
 * - Subscription change notification
 *
 * @see https://react.email
 */

